snippet.title: [ F.E.A.R ] MMod - Version 2 Release Trailer
snippet.description:
If you like my work, consider supporting me on Patreon! : https://www.patreon.com/GunshipMarkII

http://www.moddb.com/mods/fear-mmod

The second version of F.E.A.R. MMod, with even more effects, sounds, gore and entirely new weapon, laser machine-gun, which is obtainable during campaign. A lot of effects has been fixed, a lot has been added, balance now is little bit more sane, less broken everything, code is rewritten from scratch. I can explain what's new all the freaking day, just download and play it, FEAR is a great horror shooter.
